---
title: Creamy Garlic Fish Pasta with Spinach and Peas
description: This is a quick, wholesome pasta dish the whole family will enjoy. Soft, flaky barramundi tossed in a garlicky, buttery sauce with delicious greens will delight even the pickiest eater!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-garlic-fish-pasta-d4000e12.jpg
